                                                                            <comments>
                            <comment id="50699" author="nedbass" created="Thu, 17 Jan 2013 13:21:16 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;FYI, we ran into MDS stack overflow problems running debug builds last year.  Unfortunately we never fixed them, instead we just stopped using --enable-debug.  So you may want to be on the lookout for that if you pursue this issue.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="50694" author="bzzz" created="Thu, 17 Jan 2013 12:49:56 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I think we can&apos;t actually do this until &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-2160&quot; title=&quot;Implement ZFS dmu_tx_hold_append() declarations for llog &quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-2160&quot;&gt;LU-2160&lt;/a&gt; is resolved (at least).&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="29900" author="prakash" created="Mon, 27 Feb 2012 19:57:15 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;And I&apos;ve filed the second hit ASSERT as ORI-543.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
